caption.title:
Time-kill curves with CCeo against a carbapenem and polymyxin-resistant 
   K. aerogenes strain. 
   CCeo:
   Cinnamomum cassia L. essential oil; 
   MIC: minimum inhibitory concentration; 
   PMB: polymyxin B; 
   TGC: tigecycline; 
   C+: positive control (tigecycline at twice the MIC value); 
   C-: negative control (
   K. aerogenes and brain heart infusion broth).
